<h3 id="put-scheduled-limit-change">PUT Scheduled Limit Change</h3>

<p>Update a scheduled limit change on a service binding</p>
<pre class="highlight shell"><code>curl <span class="s2">"https://example.com/api/bindings/540f43bc-b9cc-4126-97a4-a56b64052da4/scheduled_limit_changes/4ff80e73-5cde-4430-936a-dcbc7f0b7c18"</span> <span class="se">\ </span>
    -X PUT <span class="se">\ </span>
    -H <span class="s2">"Authorization: Bearer UAA_ACCESS_TOKEN"</span> <span class="se">\ </span>
    -d <span class="s1">'{
  "guid": "bdb345ab-8c04-4547-9938-d1a857943f6a",
  "executes_at": "2021-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "min_instances": 2,
  "max_instances": 5,
  "recurrence": 1,
  "enabled": true
}'</span>
</code></pre>
<pre class="highlight plaintext"><code>Example Response
</code></pre>
<pre class="highlight http"><code><span class="k">HTTP</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="m">1.1</span> <span class="m">200</span> <span class="ne">OK</span>
<span class="s">{</span>
<span class="s">  "guid": "68ce3761-dbe5-4804-5fee-0ef90fdcb854",</span>
<span class="s">  "executes_at": "2016-10-25T23:00:00Z",</span>
<span class="s">  "created_at": "2021-01-01T00:00:00Z",</span>
<span class="s">  "updated_at": "2021-01-01T00:00:00Z",</span>
<span class="s">  "min_instances": 1,</span>
<span class="s">  "max_instances": 3,</span>
<span class="s">  "service_binding_guid": "540f43bc-b9cc-4126-97a4-a56b64052da4",</span>
<span class="s">  "recurrence": 0,</span>
<span class="s">  "enabled": true,</span>
<span class="s">  "links": {</span>
<span class="s">    "self": {</span>
<span class="s">      "href": "/api/bindings/540f43bc-b9cc-4126-97a4-a56b64052da4/scheduled_limit_changes/68ce3761-dbe5-4804-5fee-0ef90fdcb854"</span>
<span class="s">    },</span>
<span class="s">    "service_binding": {</span>
<span class="s">      "href": "/api/bindings/540f43bc-b9cc-4126-97a4-a56b64052da4"</span>
<span class="s">    }</span>
<span class="s">  }</span>
<span class="s">}</span>
</code></pre>

<h4 id="http-request">HTTP Request</h4>

<p><code class="prettyprint">PUT /api/bindings/{binding_guid}/scheduled_limit_changes/{change_guid}</code></p>

